{"tid":510829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南極小屋發現百年蛋糕　貌似仍可食用","createTime":"2017-12-27T00:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T04:13:58.000Z","uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8176a1a173df9711a5f7f96a6a3827d3e4e8ce","tid":510829,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"堪稱堅不可摧，南極阿代爾角一小屋日前發現一塊有100年之久蛋糕，這塊蛋糕在地球上最乾燥最寒冷且最多風的地方放了一世紀之久，看起來似乎尚未腐壞。<br />\n從事20世紀初南極研究人員文物保護工作的紐西蘭南極遺產信託基金會（Antarctic Heritage Trust）表示，研究人員在南極東部阿代爾角的一座小屋內發現一塊100年前保存完好的蛋糕。<br />\n基金會表示，這塊由亨帕餅乾（Huntley &amp; Palmers）生產的水果蛋糕有一層紙質外包裝，放在一個錫盒內。儘管錫盒包裝已有破損，但蛋糕本身看起來和聞起來幾乎都可以食用。 　　<br />\n預計這塊蛋糕是1910至1913年間英國探險家羅伯特史考特（Robert Falcon Scott）率領探險隊員乘坐特拉諾瓦號赴南極探險時帶去的。史考特和隊員們到達南極，卻喪命於返程途中。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170812/640_b5f521db83431a15a2f03763f4525d43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170812%2F640_b5f521db83431a15a2f03763f4525d43.jpg&h=371d21c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170812/640_aa1cfb9bcc8baaa814d7de64c5b7159e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170812%2F640_aa1cfb9bcc8baaa814d7de64c5b7159e.jpg&h=5021d659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170812/640_2f6a65edd23f140079573389ed872bf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170812%2F640_2f6a65edd23f140079573389ed872bf1.jpg&h=ea487611&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5e40f5a487dde1906b4ce06409fb7a87556ddc2","tid":510829,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:33:59.000Z","msg":"蛋糕俠"},{"pid":"d3b7896f7b329f333deb2b5a8922288f53ae40e6","tid":510829,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T00:34:25.